  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT83">
<l>vēntarāy viṇṇavarāy viṇṇākit taṇṇaḷiyāy</l>
<l>māntarāy mātāymaṟ ṟellāmāy cārntavarkkut</l>
<l>taṉṉāṟṟāṉ nēmiyāṉ mālvaṇṇaṉ tāṉkoṭukkum</l>
<l>piṉṉāltāṉ ceyyum pitir.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[The Lord] with the discus, the Black-hued [Lord] becomes [all] the kings,</l>
<l>the celestials, heaven, mercy [itself], the people, the mother, everything else,</l>
<l>to those who depend upon [Him]. [And yet] not [feeling] satisfied,</l>
<l>He Himself gives [all and] then, [He] does acts of wonder.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
